{"tid":1470713,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"「以正視聽」其實民意基礎無比堅固 堅固過地核 無需要過分擔心點點點","createTime":"2019-08-14T06:21:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T06:46:08.000Z","uid":34279,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ad03b7de4b040b4a3f6e22e8c02d112994b167ae","tid":1470713,"uid":34279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:21:54.000Z","msg":"民意基礎無比堅固 堅固過地核 根本陣營已成熟成形 年青人成日諗民意 無意思<br />\n<br />\n學習民建聯 無限放大對自己有利嘅文字畫面 不利嘅圓滑應對不跟進<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外眼見好多人（三毛五毛）開始因爲小事不停互相純屌純批評 其實對事件無實質幫助 <br />\n<br />\n反而更需要大家去平心討論 用一個平等嘅態度提出討論同建議<br />\n再互相學習改善<br />\n<br />\n同一條船 互相尊重"},{"pid":"188720e56aca45f48f2a3d822a57fd9e2380e0a9","tid":1470713,"uid":34279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:22:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"546183c5d27bc80cd17853619ebf33d8d3b95ddf","tid":1470713,"uid":34279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:22:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"70ac688b0a61a49e043713b492010e2d4bbf7489","tid":1470713,"uid":34279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:23:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f38d0bd5bf09093861dce2ffdf8d2dc32ff44636","tid":1470713,"uid":34279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:24:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"585b71cd60c2f92ac65668dfcf214d713e1d5f9d","tid":1470713,"uid":34279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:24:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1930f3f4f56e2b8f1e9c17df9007fba5fae84a72","tid":1470713,"uid":34279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:25:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"97fb9c626e3d26cf53443f19e650847872cfebab","tid":1470713,"uid":34279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:25:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"89fe13a5cc0bfb2321dd65f35d42e7180d12dc2a","tid":1470713,"uid":34279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:25:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bd51e2bf72e0